    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900390/extras/f6e2c5f993801b13ac4914252597bb1b.poster.avif?t=1710028308\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900390/extras/f6e2c5f993801b13ac4914252597bb1b.webm?t=1710028308\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900390/extras/f6e2c5f993801b13ac4914252597bb1b.mp4?t=1710028308\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the fishing locations of Cradle Lake and avoid its dangers using your small but maneuverable motorboat.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Catch fish through in depth fishing mechanics using your fishing rod and selection of lures. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Uncover the story of Cradle Lake through lore and environmental story telling found in each level.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An original in game soundtrack by Nathan Hanover.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 different levels to explore.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In depth fishing mechanics that take inspiration from classic fishing games.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A player controlled boat used to explore each level.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adjustable graphics settings to mimic the look of older systems(can also be turned off).</li></ul>",
